
In the INDEX dir is the following files:

 * fulltext: the complete uri and body of every file scanned.
 * docmap: marshalled ruby array of 
     1. array of uris, indexed by doc id, 
     2. array of 4-tuples of [offsets within the fulltext, doc ids, field ids, data size]
 * suffixes: look more into how this is formatted
 * field: sorted list of field names